<span class="header1">Business/Management paired with Science/Mathematics (CH)</span>

<p>If your scores on this pairing were high, you naturally understand that there are always ways to improve a situation. You can probably handle several tasks at one time. People like you have made important contributions in business. You are an excellent thinker.  You are also likely to be a no-nonsense kind of person. You are mentally creative and like to ask the question, "Why?" Because of this, you will look for new business ventures.</p>
<p>Most occupations in this pairing require at least a Bachelor's Degree or some post high school courses. For some jobs, it may be valuable to have a Master's Degree or a Ph.D.</p>

